data.description: Reduced!! Charming two bedroom, two bath home is located on a beautiful treed corner lot with views of one of the many ponds in the community. This home features a split floor plan, vinyl plank flooring throughout except for the kitchen and bathrooms, vaulted ceilings, breakfast nook, attached storage room, newer appliances and a well for the timed irrigation system. Enjoy nature and serenity from your screened back porch. Recent improvements include roof replacement June 2022, new HVAC 2019 and rescreening the back porch.  A must see, all measurements approximate. Own your own property, not a rental community. Lighthouse Cove is a beautiful, gated community with a large heated swimming pool, club house (currently under renovation), tennis and pickle ball courts, shuffle board courts, boat launch for shallow water boats, recreational picnic area on the river, fishing pier and fenced boat/RV storage (storage fees apply).  Golf carts are a second means of transportation. It is a boating/fishing paradise located a short distance from the Mosquito Lagoon. Get lost in the local backwaters (Canaveral Seashore/Merritt Island Wildlife Refuge) in your Kayak or Boat. Watch the rocket launches from the community fishing pier or from your own backyard. Don't miss out. A great opportunity to live in paradise!!! This home will not last long. ;Water: City
